bled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":29358,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/tilawat-al-quran-beautiful-voice\/","url_meta":{"origin":17034,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Tilawah: Reciting the Quran aloud in a pleasant voice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah does not listen to anything as he does to the beautiful voice of a prophet, reciting the Quran aloud pleasantly.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7544, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 792 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17030,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/recite-quran-regularly\/","url_meta":{"origin":17034,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Recite the Quran regularly, or you will forget","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the parable of the companion of the Quran is that of a tied camel. If he is committed to it, he will keep it. If he releases it, he will lose it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32625,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/03\/allah-mercy-lut-yusuf\/","url_meta":{"origin":17034,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Lut: May Allah have mercy on Prophet Lot","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy upon Lot. He had sought refuge in a strong pillar. If I had remained in prison for as long as Joseph, I would have accepted an offer of freedom.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8141,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/preferred-tashahhud-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":17034,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Variants of Prayer&#8217;s ending supplication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would teach us the testimony of faith in prayer, just as he would teach us a chapter from the Quran. The Prophet would say, \u201cGreetings, blessings, prayers, and good words are for Allah. Peace be upon you,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5963,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/07\/tafsir-quran-bil-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":17034,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tafsir: The Prophet explains the Quran with the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah reported: When the verse was revealed, \u201cThose who have faith and do not mix their faith with wrong,\u201d (6:82), we said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, who among us has not mixed his faith with wrong?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is not as you\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17032,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/not-say-deliberately-forgot-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":17034,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Do not say I deliberately forgot the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWretched is one who says: I have forgotten such a verse. Rather, he was made to forget it. Strive to remember the Quran, for it is quicker to escape the hearts of men than camels.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17034","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.a